### Managers & Clients

- Project Manager - The individual managing the project, the default selection is the name of the individual setting up the project. This can be changed.
- Assistant Manager - (If required) If you wish to associate a co-worker who is working on the project, they will also get notifications.
- Client selection - (if required) It is possible to associate any project with any clients you have added via the Client Menu option along the extreme left of the screen. (Add Menu image)